    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"bureaucratic bloat\" is such a vague thing to use to dismiss a whole system. can you be more specific? it feels like you're giving equal weight to a valid way to ensure survival versus just an economic preference for private industry. isn't there a fundamental moral difference there that makes one side more \"correct\" than the other?",
